Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.45,0:00:02.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.30,0:00:06.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This DVD is specially made by Shogakukan for everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.72,0:00:10.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When watching this DVD, please watch in a bright room and sit away from the TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.48,0:00:12.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kaitou Kid!?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.82,0:00:36.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What would you like for dinner, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.72,0:00:38.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anything is fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.37,0:00:43.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Honestly, I really want to make sukiyaki, but my dad hasn't had much work lately,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.47,0:00:45.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So we have to save our money a bit...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.34,0:00:48.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}! Today we have a discount on beef.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.23,0:00:51.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then I guess today I'll make a croquette.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.64,0:00:54.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can I have 150... I mean 100 grams, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.03,0:00:56.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And eggs as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.76,0:00:57.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,With joy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.92,0:00:59.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}, who is this child?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.73,0:01:02.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, he lives with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.17,0:01:05.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's not Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s illegitimate son, is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.90,0:01:07.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way, auntie.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.18,0:01:09.60,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.40,0:01:12.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here, 20 grams bonus from us.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.70,0:01:14.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.91,0:01:20.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Potatoes, onions, cabbage, tomatoes...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.23,0:01:22.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}, this is from us.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.15,0:01:24.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.67,0:01:28.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But who would have thought that Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r} had a little brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.07,0:01:30.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, it's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.75,0:01:37.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come in everyone! Cheap fish!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.56,0:01:38.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.39,0:01:40.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess we'll have that for lunch tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.66,0:01:43.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You look good as always, Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.50,0:01:46.15,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Speaking of which, Ran...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.47,0:01:48.18,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}She always went shopping like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.98,0:02:09.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here, keep some of these shijimi clams.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.21,0:02:12.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thanks! Now I can make miso soup!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.09,0:02:15.49,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}But she's just as popular.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.24,0:02:19.45,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}This is "Cooking with Ookino Yoko"...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.86,0:02:23.33,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Our guess today is Detective Mouri Kogoro{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-san{\r\be10}.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.65,0:02:25.68,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Well then, until next week!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.57,0:02:28.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bye-bye, Yoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.38,0:02:34.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Jeez, how many times does he need to watch that video before he's satisfied?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.45,0:02:36.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That tape is probably already worn out.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.65,0:02:38.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.11,0:02:42.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's wrong? It's not like there's a client...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.37,0:02:47.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.12,0:02:49.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.89,0:02:55.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.76,0:02:58.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is that, Dad? From whom?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.47,0:03:00.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.06,0:03:03.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The parcel is just for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.53,0:03:05.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know but from whom?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.66,0:03:07.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No one!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.13,0:03:10.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you order it yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.81,0:03:12.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that so, Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.56,0:03:18.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait, Dad! Could it be it's something weird, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.29,0:03:22.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Idiot! What are you talking about?\NIt is something for work.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.26,0:03:24.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then why are you going upstairs?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.17,0:03:25.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're so annoying!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.09,0:03:30.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What about you, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.00,0:03:32.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's look suspicious?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.14,0:03:35.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right? There must be something...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.13,0:03:41.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.24,0:03:43.34,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Have you prepared the money?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.66,0:03:44.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.41,0:03:47.12,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Don't "eh" to me, have you prepared the...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.44,0:03:48.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who are you!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.20,0:03:50.12,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Blackmailer.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.44,0:03:50.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Record!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.00,0:03:51.66,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.98,0:03:53.89,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.21,0:03:56.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hello? Hello!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.77,0:03:59.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is it, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.63,0:04:01.63,Signs,,0,0,0,,NUMBER IS NOT AVAILABLE
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.27,0:04:01.64,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}As I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.96,0:04:02.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.53,0:04:06.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Blackmail phone call?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.81,0:04:11.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But the phone number was not displayed, so we cannot call him back.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.77,0:04:15.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And he didn't give any name, did he?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.86,0:04:21.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since he called here by accident, the number he meant to call is probably similar to this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.79,0:04:24.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad, we should hurry up and call the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.63,0:04:28.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Quiet, quiet, all you said is empty talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.19,0:04:31.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not certain that there's been a crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.50,0:04:32.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.87,0:04:35.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe it was just the tax collector calling.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.97,0:04:38.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I promised to play mahjong.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.50,0:04:41.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait, you should listen to what Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} said!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.10,0:04:44.82,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Of course, there is no certainty that this is a crime, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.14,0:04:48.48,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}If this is a kidnapping, then there is no time to waste.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.80,0:04:50.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.39,0:04:51.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.19,0:04:53.21,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}But before that...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.99,0:04:56.83,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Have you prepared the money?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.15,0:04:59.86,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Don't "eh" to me, have you prepared the...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.18,0:05:01.15,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Who are you!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.48,0:05:05.46,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That voice... I've heard it before...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.78,0:05:07.11,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Also...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.43,0:05:08.10,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.42,0:05:08.92,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.24,0:05:13.68,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I think I've already heard that voice somewhere, but where?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.57,0:05:18.79,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Wait a minute, the only voices I've heard recently...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.11,0:05:20.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Jeez...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.85,0:05:22.77,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Cheap fish!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.09,0:05:23.87,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.19,0:05:26.51,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}You look good as always, Ran{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-chan{\r\be10}.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.83,0:05:28.95,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Today we have a discount on beef.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.27,0:05:32.07,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He's not Mouri{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-san{\r\be10}'s illegitimate son, is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.39,0:05:34.85,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Cabbage, tomatoes...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.17,0:05:38.68,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}But who would have thought that Ran{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-chan{\r\be10} had a little brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.25,0:05:41.56,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What if it was...!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.19,0:05:44.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's because ours is pesticide-free!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.66,0:05:47.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You will definitely like it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.40,0:05:50.38,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}It's not. A bit similar, but not that voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.70,0:05:51.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you for your purchase.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.27,0:05:54.63,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Where? Where did I hear?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.58,0:05:59.42,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.74,0:06:02.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hello, sorry to bother you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.94,0:06:06.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm Mouriwaki from DM Trading Company. Is the chief in?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.30,0:06:18.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Heiji{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-niichan{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.20,0:06:24.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kudou... I mean Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.00,0:06:31.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To call me in all the way from Osaka, there must be very important, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.41,0:06:32.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.07,0:06:34.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.77,0:06:39.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Blackmail phone call?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.39,0:06:43.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, he said that the caller's voice and yours are identical.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.21,0:06:47.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I though I had heard that voice somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.68,0:06:51.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But the way he talked was different, so I didn't recognize it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.97,0:06:54.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the reason we called you to...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.70,0:06:59.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Find out who the man was trying to call by having me speak in his manner.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.66,0:07:05.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And after we trying all the number similar to the detective agency.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.12,0:07:08.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We will judge from their reaction.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.81,0:07:10.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right, as I expected from Hattori{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.29,0:07:11.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kudou...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.89,0:07:15.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, no, no! Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, it seemed like your way of thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.93,0:07:20.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We already have a list of phone numbers so I think it'd be best if we hurried.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.65,0:07:27.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If so, let's get started!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.85,0:07:32.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can you leave the rest to me and the kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.26,0:07:38.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then I'll cook for dinner. If you need help, just ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.99,0:07:49.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Prepare dinner?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.77,0:07:52.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What a homely detective agency, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.57,0:07:54.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, save the jokes for later. Let's start!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.22,0:07:56.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.41,0:08:07.19,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Hello, this is Inoue.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.45,0:08:16.12,Signs,,0,0,0,,Hattori first says "ya" at the end, then corrects it to "da". The first option is the Osaka dialect, the second is the classic one.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.78,0:08:10.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is me. Eh... It's me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.98,0:08:12.67,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Huh? Who is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.99,0:08:14.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I must have a wrong number.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.20,0:08:20.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.98,0:08:21.36,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.68,0:08:24.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,S-Sorry, I have a wrong number.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.07,0:08:28.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uh, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.21,0:08:34.73,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Hello, this is Yuwatsume.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.05,0:08:35.45,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.77,0:08:36.68,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Oh, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.38,0:08:41.40,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What else do you want? You dirty thief!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.72,0:08:45.25,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I handed over 10 million yen and haven't spoken with the police as we agreed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.57,0:08:47.55,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}You shouldn't have any more business with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.87,0:08:48.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll call you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.23,0:08:52.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bingo, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.57,0:08:58.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,From what we heard, he has already paid out the money and completed the deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.39,0:09:01.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But he called him a dirty thief.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.51,0:09:03.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What exactly did he mean by "thief"?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.76,0:09:09.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.44,0:09:15.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.75,0:09:17.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector Nakamori.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.84,0:09:20.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You are from Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s place...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.95,0:09:23.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you visit Yuwatsume{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.69,0:09:25.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who is Yuwatsume?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.75,0:09:28.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We are investigating a fraud case.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.17,0:09:34.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A jewelry robbery?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.77,0:09:37.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, Yuwatsume is a rare name, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.99,0:09:42.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So we looked on the internet and found out that Yuwatsume works as a jewel broker.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.26,0:09:46.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which means that it was likely a jewel robbery.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.63,0:09:49.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But we're not sure what it has to do with the blackmail.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.72,0:09:52.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Alright! Let's meet this Yuwatsume.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.18,0:09:55.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, inspector.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.48,0:10:00.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't theft covered by the 3rd division? And you are from the 2nd...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.68,0:10:04.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, since I'm already here... And I'll get in trouble if I ignore the jewel thief.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.62,0:10:11.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.84,0:10:13.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.54,0:10:15.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have an idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.60,0:10:22.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did something just flew by?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.79,0:10:25.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, probably a giant flying squirrel.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.38,0:10:26.60,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Yeah, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.23,0:10:37.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do the police want?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.62,0:10:41.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you recognize this voice?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.17,0:10:44.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Have you prepared the money?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.46,0:10:46.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Have you caught the criminal?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.78,0:10:47.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What kind of criminal?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.42,0:10:51.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What "what"? I'm talking about the jewel thief!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.90,0:10:53.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Jewels!?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.45,0:10:54.91,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Yes, we've got him!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.23,0:10:59.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please tell us more, we need a witness statement from the victim.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.45,0:11:01.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sure, no problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.46,0:11:03.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The day before yesterday 100 million yen...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.68,0:11:06.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could you repeat that again?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.15,0:11:07.68,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.23,0:11:10.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Have you prepared the money?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.06,0:11:11.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,One more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.08,0:11:14.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Have you prepared the money?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.69,0:11:17.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, he is not a criminal!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.53,0:11:19.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He didn't have such a weird accent!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.59,0:11:22.23,Signs,,0,0,0,,Hattori's Kansai dialect comes through even when he speaks standard Japanese.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.49,0:11:24.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you mean "weird"? Are you making fun of the Kansai dialect?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.31,0:11:26.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.36,0:11:29.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.43,0:11:30.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.00,0:11:32.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I am...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.04,0:11:38.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,High school detective from Naniwa School, Hattori Heiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.78,0:11:39.96,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}You're an idiot...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.28,0:11:44.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Officer! What is the meaning of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.00,0:11:48.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anyway, the thing is, 100 million yen worth of jewel was stolen, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.29,0:11:52.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, it hasn't been stolen.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.73,0:11:54.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.91,0:12:01.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here's the proof.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.96,0:12:03.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But a minute ago you said...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.27,0:12:05.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was a joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.26,0:12:08.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Joke?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.33,0:12:10.71,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I see. So that's how it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.03,0:12:19.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's it, then. That jewel was stolen, but he offered to return it if you paid him 10 million yen, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.99,0:12:22.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way! Why would I...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.61,0:12:26.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The point is, you've already sold it to someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.04,0:12:31.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And even at a value of 10 million yen, the jewel would be worth returning.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.18,0:12:34.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Am I right, Yuwatsume{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.63,0:12:38.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yuwatsume{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, please tell us the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.79,0:12:42.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If we don't arrest the criminal now, it's possible he might strike again.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.16,0:12:46.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe a second or even third time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.72,0:12:49.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right, just like Kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.32,0:12:50.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kid!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.50,0:12:55.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right! I have a lot of bad memories because of him!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.78,0:12:59.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn it! I will not forgive you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.36,0:13:00.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.10,0:13:05.60,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Speaking of which, I wonder if he'll come for this jewel.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.92,0:13:08.14,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Wait, this jewel...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.46,0:13:10.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This criminal is not very greedy, is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.09,0:13:13.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who is this boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.32,0:13:16.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's been bothering me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.54,0:13:18.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, please don't mind of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.44,0:13:23.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For a 100 million yen jewel, he only got 10 million yen, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.73,0:13:26.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If I were in his place, I would have asked for at least half the cost.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.96,0:13:30.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's really strange that he only took 10%.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.62,0:13:34.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Perhaps the jewel you have traded back is a fake?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.78,0:13:35.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.37,0:13:43.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,E-Excuse me for a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.12,0:13:54.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a fake...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.33,0:13:58.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.79,0:14:01.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It looks like this is a fraud case, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.04,0:14:05.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you admit it now, Yuwatsume{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.56,0:14:06.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.64,0:14:08.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, do you have any clue about the criminal?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.30,0:14:15.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,About that, even when we exchanged the money, we didn't meet in person. I only heard his voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.16,0:14:18.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was it from the phone? Did you record the conversation?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.28,0:14:20.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, I didn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.67,0:14:31.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems like the old man and the girl are already asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.15,0:14:34.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hattori...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.00,0:14:37.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, I know, you don't have to say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.72,0:14:41.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you want me to recreate our phone conversation with him, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.80,0:14:45.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, since this is not the real voice of the criminal, it will not work as evidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.30,0:14:48.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But that should help us find him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.65,0:14:49.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.99,0:14:51.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's get start.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.21,0:14:56.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Have {\i1}ya{\i0} prepared the money?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.06,0:15:00.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, not like that. "Have {\i1}you{\i0} prepared the money?"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.58,0:15:02.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't that what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.64,0:15:06.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not, that's why Yuwatsume{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} figured you out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.48,0:15:10.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on, one more time, "Have you prepared the money?"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.74,0:15:12.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Have {\i1}ya{\i0} prepared the money?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.51,0:15:16.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not like that! Why can't you talk like me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.78,0:15:20.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can help it. I've been in Osaka since I was born.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.32,0:15:24.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Jeez, at this rate, you will never say it right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.49,0:15:26.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So what if I can't say it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.64,0:15:30.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You cannot speak in Osaka dialect, it's the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.47,0:15:34.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not the same thing. Of course I can speak Osaka dialect.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.15,0:15:40.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really? You've tried to speak Osaka dialect before.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.03,0:15:42.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Using my voice, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.46,0:15:46.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The voice-changing bowtie!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.20,0:15:50.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right! We could only take one try with that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.64,0:15:52.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why didn't I think about this earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.21,0:15:56.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So this is what it means, "See no farther than your nose", huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.70,0:15:59.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hattori, you can go home now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.19,0:16:01.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kudou!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.53,0:16:02.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.08,0:16:08.26,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Please listen to the voice of the suspect relating to the jewel theft.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.87,0:16:10.04,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Have you prepared the money?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.45,0:16:13.81,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Don't "eh" to me, have you prepared the...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.13,0:16:15.63,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Who are you!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.95,0:16:20.47,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Those who can identify the suspect's voice...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.22,0:16:25.13,Signs,,0,0,0,,Please call the special number...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.76,0:16:26.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was Hattori{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}'s voice, right?\NYour standard Japanese accent is very good.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.71,0:16:30.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, yes. I am a detective after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.76,0:16:33.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I'm surprised they didn't catch you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.14,0:16:38.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector Nakamori realized that it was Heiji{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-niichan{\r}'s voice right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.63,0:16:43.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Exactly, but even knowing that, he used his judgment to put it air on TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.14,0:16:46.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That old man has a lot of guts.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.37,0:16:58.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thanks to the widespread influence of TV, all viewers will immediately rush to call.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.53,0:16:59.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's Kazuha.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.56,0:17:00.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.17,0:17:03.43,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Heiji!!! What are you doing!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.75,0:17:06.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your voice was just on TV!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.83,0:17:10.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It spoke some weird Tokyo Japanese accent, but it was definitely your voice!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.89,0:17:13.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is your family has big financial problems that you have to stole the jewelry!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.02,0:17:17.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You idiot! There's no way I'll steal the jewel!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.85,0:17:20.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But even if you say that...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.70,0:17:23.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't talk nonsense!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.61,0:17:26.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They all rushed to call, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.63,0:17:28.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, really...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.40,0:17:34.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By the way, Kudou, did you remember where you heard that "good morning!"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.99,0:17:36.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's the key to the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.77,0:17:39.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, but I've been thinking about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.69,0:17:43.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now, as I recall, it was more muffled than the man's voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.67,0:17:44.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.25,0:17:46.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wonder what this is...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.41,0:17:51.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Ookino Yoko's Special Figurine Alarm Clock"?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.55,0:17:53.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.27,0:17:57.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't that what Uncle brought yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.70,0:18:02.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't believe it. What is this for?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.39,0:18:07.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can I take a look?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.55,0:18:10.68,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Wait a minute, Ookino Yoko...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.10,0:18:13.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is well made, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.60,0:18:14.16,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.90,0:18:16.88,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}It's morning, please wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.20,0:18:19.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's that voice!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.63,0:18:22.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r}, this is the voice from that call!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.39,0:18:26.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't touch her!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.12,0:18:31.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is a specially made clock that available only for Yoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r} fan club members.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.62,0:18:35.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad, how much did it cost?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.12,0:18:38.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Does it matter how much it cost?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.51,0:18:39.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How much was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.28,0:18:42.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,2... 2000 yen...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.28,0:18:45.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're lying!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.66,0:18:47.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,20,000 yen...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.36,0:18:50.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,20,000 yen? I've been taking daily wages into account just to get by!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.29,0:18:53.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And you spent that much for a toy!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.45,0:18:55.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why you're hiding it from us, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.18,0:19:01.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Only 200 of them were made. And I wanted just one so badly...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.52,0:19:02.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.23,0:19:06.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Only 200 of them were made?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.36,0:19:09.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We can get his name from the fan club.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.46,0:19:14.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, the criminal probably bought the clock and set the wrong time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.90,0:19:16.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So when he was talking to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.02,0:19:17.66,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.98,0:19:18.81,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.09,0:19:21.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hello? Hello!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.87,0:19:33.13,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The next day, thanks to a fan club list and a call from one of the viewers, we found the thief.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.07,0:19:44.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.83,0:19:48.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If anyone come any closer, I'll throw it this into the sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.73,0:19:52.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn it...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.83,0:19:55.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His voice really does sound like mine...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.26,0:20:05.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.94,0:20:22.75,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Good morning! It's morning already! Please wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.07,0:20:25.74,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Good morning! It's morning already! Please wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.68,0:20:55.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why is Kid...?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.84,0:20:59.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Most likely, Kid also want the jewel as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.09,0:21:04.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was probably him that was there before the interview.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.83,0:21:06.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's how he knew the time of this case...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.70,0:21:12.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That wasn't a flying squirrel...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.80,0:21:18.45,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Congratulations, little detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.77,0:21:21.20,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}And you too, Detective of the West.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.37,0:21:25.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Kid is getting away!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.35,0:21:34.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So this is what we called: "Having your fried tofu taken by a kite", I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.82,0:21:37.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is this what I left Osaka for?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.80,0:21:40.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.62,0:21:44.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What an idiot... I'm going home.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.24,0:21:47.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.65,0:22:32.40,Signs,,0,0,0,,Whimsical Kaitou Kid: Returns 100 Million Yen Jewel to the Owner
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.83,0:22:38.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}, one more! Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.27,0:22:43.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No! From now on, no smoking\Nand only one beer per day!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.12,0:22:46.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No! Such a waste of life!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.46,0:22:52.00,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}This is a very homely detective agency, isn't it?
